name: Leather "Feather" Earrings
description:
Handmade leather and suede earrings in the shape of feathers. Earrings are approximately 6 in/16 cm in length and are all hand cut, so there will be a small bit of variation in shape and size. The earrings consist of two pieces, one large "feather" of leather and a smaller "feather" of suede, in a single color. Due to natural variations in leather and suede the texture may be slightly different than what is shown in the pictures, depending on the hides I have available. You can choose either gold-tone or silver-tone for the rings and hooks of the earrings.

**I will have other color options coming soon. If you are interested in a particular color before then, please contact me to see if I have it available**

name: Silver-leafed Bird Bone Choker
description: This choker is made from a bird vertebra, collected from nature, which has been silver-leafed in real sterling silver. Hand-drilled and then attached to a small silver chain using silver jump rings, it is finished with a lobster claw clasp. I only have a few of these particular bones (i.e. of the same shape and from the same skeleton) so this is a limited edition piece.
